%     -2*K^2*b^2*beta^2*eta^2*pL+4*K^2*b^2*beta^2*eta*pL*r-2*K^2*b^2*beta^2*pL*r^2 ...
%     +K^2*b^2*beta^2*eta^2-2*K^2*b^2*beta^2*eta*r+K^2*b^2*beta^2*r^2-2*K*alpha*b*beta*eta*pL*r ...
